OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784607479
OL,3,CIs a fourth UK heatwave brewing?
OL,5,FAfter a two-week heatwave which
OL,6,Fbrought temperatures of 30C or more,
OL,7,Fit has finally started to cool down
OL,8,Ffor most of the UK.
OL,10,FBut this brief respite of cooler
OL,11,Fweather is not expected to last much
OL,12,Flonger than this week.
OL,14,FWhat can we expect this week?
OL,16,FSimilar to the weekend, it will remain
OL,17,Fmostly settled with spells of sunshine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
