PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784607479
OL,3,CIs a fourth UK heatwave brewing?
OL,5,FSome forecasts suggest this will bring
OL,6,Fsome heavier and more significant
OL,7,Frain, much needed in many locations
OL,8,Fafter a remarkably dry few weeks.
OL,10,FWill there be another heatwave?
OL,12,FThe long-range forecast shows signs of
OL,13,Fanother heatwave brewing at the start
OL,14,Fof August.
OL,16,FTraditionally, we see our highest
OL,17,Ftemperatures at this time of year
OL,18,Fafter the ground and air have had the
OL,19,Fmaximum time to heat up during the
OL,20,Fsummer months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
