PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784607479
OL,3,CIs a fourth UK heatwave brewing?
OL,5,FForecasts are showing another area of
OL,6,Fhigh pressure building in the first
OL,7,Fweekend of August - it is very similar
OL,8,Fto the type of weather we had earlier
OL,9,Fthis month.
OL,11,FIt will become established from the
OL,12,Fsouth and west and bring dry settled
OL,13,Fconditions.
OL,15,FWith the sunshine, temperatures will
OL,16,Fbe rising day on day with increasingly
OL,17,Fwarmer nights again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
