PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784607479
OL,3,CIs a fourth UK heatwave brewing?
OL,5,FUnlike June's heatwave, which was
OL,6,Fcaused by hot humid air drawn in from
OL,7,FEurope, this is likely to come from
OL,8,Fsomething forecasters call "home grown
OL,9,Fheat" meaning it comes from the UK.
OL,11,FThe details are subject to change when
OL,12,Fit comes to timing and how high
OL,13,Ftemperatures will climb.
OL,15,FWe will get more clarity in the coming
OL,16,Fdays.
